  "text": "CBs were deposited at the entrance of a microchannel (figure 7-2) using the developed interface, or manually using forceps. Although the connecting Teflon ® tube was flush with the microchannel inner diameter, CBs were positioned 2-3 mm from the entrance so fluid flow was fully developed after it transitioned through this connection point [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
